powerpc: replace CONFIG_DEBUG_KERNEL with CONFIG_DEBUG_MISC

CONFIG_DEBUG_KERNEL should not impact code generation.  Use the newly
defined CONFIG_DEBUG_MISC instead to keep the current code.

